query:
DELETE sr FROM seasonalRates sr
JOIN sites s ON sr.siteId = s.id
JOIN shopping_centres c ON s.centreId = c.id
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Chullora%'
AND sr.startDate <= '2026-06-14'
AND sr.endDate >= '2026-06-13';
